  "remarks": "JSC Moscow Machine-Building Plant “Vpered” is one of the oldest enterprises in the Russian aviation industry, operating since 1931. The company is a leading company producing tail rotors and blades for helicopters of the Mi family, which are widely used by the Russian armed forces during Russia’s war of aggression on Ukraine.",
